    <sect1>
        <title>Oracle RAC Installation</title>

        <para>The following sections explain how to perform your Oracle RAC installation.</para>

        <sect2>
            <title>Installing Oracle Grid Infrastructure</title>

            <para>Log in to the SUSE Linux Enterprise Server 12 64-bit OS as a non-administration
                user. Download the Oracle Database 12c Release 1 Grid Infrastructure (12.1.0.2.0)
                for Linux x86-64.</para>

            <para>Extract <filename>grid.zip</filename> and run the installer
                    <application>'./runInstaller'</application> from Grid ShipHome.</para>


            <para>Follow the steps below:</para>

            <procedure>

                <step>
                    <para>Select <emphasis role="strong">Installation Option</emphasis>.</para>

                    <figure>
                        <title>Select Installation Option </title>
                        <mediaobject>
                            <imageobject role="fo">
                                <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-install-option.png" width="70%"
                                    format="PNG"/>
                            </imageobject>
                            <imageobject role="html">
                                <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-install-option.png" width="80%"
                                    format="PNG"/>
                            </imageobject>
                        </mediaobject>
                    </figure>

                    <para>Choose the option <emphasis role="strong">Install and Configure Oracle
                            Grid Infrastructure for a Cluster</emphasis>", then click <emphasis
                            role="strong">Next</emphasis> to continue.</para>

                </step>


                <step>
                    <para>Select <emphasis role="strong">Cluster Type</emphasis>.</para>


                    <figure>
                        <title>Select Installation Option </title>
                        <mediaobject>
                            <imageobject role="fo">
                                <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-cluster-type.png" width="70%"
                                    format="PNG"/>
                            </imageobject>
                            <imageobject role="html">
                                <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-cluster-type.png" width="80%"
                                    format="PNG"/>
                            </imageobject>
                        </mediaobject>
                    </figure>

                    <para>Choose option <emphasis role="strong">Configure a Standard
                            Cluster</emphasis>", then click <emphasis role="strong">Next</emphasis>
                        to continue.</para>
                </step>

                <step>
                    <para>Select <emphasis role="strong">Installation Type</emphasis>.</para>

                    <figure>
                        <title>Select Installation Option </title>
